In an effort to make a decision, they have asked us to answer the question by the end of this week if we can
support their three areas of asks below.

I have included internal notes that you can choose to read to get more detail behind each of their asks.

1.  Support a Hybrid Gateway Model. (Internal Note: The most near-term model).
2.  Support a FSP Model with a 12-month conversion. (Internal Note: The secondary option).
    This would essentially eliminate the need for a gateway solution if we can commit to this timing and
    partnership model.
3.  Support a single message, auth only API solution, with tokenization, routing and format
    preservation, to support their SAP solution.
